resources.string: This application is powered by ActionBarSherlock, Apache CouchDB, ACRA, and opencsv, which are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. A copy of the Apache license may be found at http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html. The data used in this application was obtained from surveys conducted by the IPEDS.\n\n Note: If SAT or ACT scores are provided in the Matches tab, the app attempts to match you to colleges where your scores would fall roughly in the middle 50% of the student body. However, if a college does not consider the writing section of the SAT, the app disregards your writing score. If both SAT and ACT scores are provided, the app simply uses the higher of the two.
